My second map. I tried to make this map as interesting as I could at the time of me making it, which wasn't too interesting. I was drunk at the time.

Basically, both teams start out at opposite ends of the map (Duh), and there is a raised platform for snipers, but so people don't just go up there and camp I made the middle wall (Which has 2 doors on either side) high enough so snipers on the ledge could not hit people on the ground, only people on the other sniper tower. There is also a ledge about half way up from the ground to the sniper tower that spans the sides of the arena.

Aim_ag_tyr4 ----------- 12 players Description: Another skill map set within a small arena with objects placed tactically forcing you to use skill to eliminate your enemies. This is a texture map. I advise you not to jump in the pit in the middle :) I made this map to my own design and I like the extra factor the pit is giving. Objective: Use the objects and environment to beat your enemies in gunfights. Pure skill will save you from getting that one headshot you didn't deserve. You also don't deserve to fall in teh pit.

aim_ag_tyr3 ----------- 12 players Description: My third skill map. It is set within a small arena with objects placed tactically forcing you to use skill to eliminate your enemies. This is a texture map. This map is not focused on horizontal gunfights. By adding a second floor another dimension of strategy is used. I made this map to my own design. Objective: Use the objects, height and environment to beat your enemies in gunfights. Pure skill will save you from getting that one headshot you didn't deserve...

Aim_ag_tyr2 ----------- 12 players or less (preferred) Description: My second skill map. It is set within a small arena with objects placed tactically forcing you to use skill to eliminate your enemies. This is a texture map. It is a 2x2 checkerboard layout and works very well :) I made this map to my own design. Objective: Use the objects and environment to beat your enemies in gunfights. Pure skill will save you from getting that one headshot you didn't deserve...

Aim_ag_tyr ----------- 12 players+ Description: A symmetrical skill map set within a medium sized building. The objects are placed tactically so you can use it to your advantage. Both sides are exact mirrored. This is a texture map. I made this map to a design I quickly came up with and after toying around a bit it has worked out quite well. Objective: Fight your way through this symmetrical fortress and neutralize the threat that lies on the other side...
